unittitle_ssm: Reformed Church on the Heights records
abstract_ssm: This collection contains various records of the Reformed Church on the Heights dating from 1845 to 1852, including contracts, accounts, receipts, bills, and payrolls related to the construction of the Church's building, as well as deeds to the Church's land.
